# One line-ending everywhere. Normalize all text to LF in the repo and on
# checkout, so Windows desktop, phone (connector), and the Linux sandbox stop
# disagreeing about line endings. This CRLF mismatch churned 500+ files and
# helped diverge the harness across devices on 2026-07-17. Binary files are
# auto-detected and left untouched.
* text=auto eol=lf
